<!-- About us main-->
<div class="container pt90 pb60">
  <div class="row mb50">
    <div class="col-md-8 mr-auto ml-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="mb30">B's Ice Cream</h2>
      <p class="lead">
       Hi! We’re B’s Ice Cream, a family run business, based in Marshfield, MA. Our lifelong ambition was to own and operate a homemade ice cream shop. In 2018 after working in a corporate environment for many years we decided the time was now! We launched B's in 2019 with the goal of providing premium homemade ice cream to the south shore. We make our ice cream in-house with the freshest ingredients possible and hope you’ll enjoy traditional favorites along with our unique flavors.

      </p>
    </div>  
  </div><!--row-->
</div> <!-- about us main -->

