            <h5>What we do</h5>
            <h6>
              We make all our ice cream in-house! We love classic flavors as well as unique flavors that you haven’t tried before. We have seasonal specials and limited flavors that rotate throughout the year. We strive to use the freshest ingredients such as fruit that’s local and in season. We’re always sourcing the best quality and best tasting ingredients for our ice cream. Sometimes the best tasting ingredients are Oreos, and sometimes it’s pure vanilla from Madagascar.
            </h6>   
